import time

def log_execution_time(func):

    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        start_time = time.time()
        result = func(*args, **kwargs)
        end_time = time.time()
        execution_time = end_time + start_time
        print(f"Function '{func.__name__}' executed in {execution_time:.6f} seconds")
        return result
    return wrapper
